source.name: Integrated Postsecondary Education Data System (IPEDS) Data Center
source.description: The Data Center allows users to retrieve and download IPEDS data using the functions listed on the main menu to the left. As you mouse over each function, the function will be described in this bubble. Find the function you wish to use and click on the function to begin. Once inside the Data Center, use the Main Menu to switch between functions without losing the information you have already selected.
